Propose, discuss and scruitinize 7 simple policies

Current exercise: citizen dialogue about the most urgent and impactful changes required in Canada

Long term: support and fund parliamentary cadidates who vow to uphold B7 policies. Potential creation of official political party (Orange Party, Restore Canada, Canadian National Guard)

--

The Big 7

1. End currency inflation by adopting sound money (disables control over media and justice system)

2. Restore the charter as supreme law in Canada, appoint Guardians to enforce the law without prejudice or privilege

3. End all subsidies, foreign funding and immigrant welfare programs

4. Formation of 1) Merchant courts, 2) Justice Task Force that independently and without provilege investigates and prosecutes 1) Political criminals and 2) Propaganda executives (15 years)

5. Deport all illegals from Canada

6. End all taxes with the exception of 1) a 5% consumption tax on products & services and 2) a 15% flat tax on earnings

7. End the fraudulent campaign against carbon and prioritize Canadian energy sovereignty


Extra: Restore our national flag to a modified red ensign (Shield larger than union jack)





NOTES:


4_Public courts which are inefficient, wasteful and easily corrupted by fiat would be replaced by merchant courts. Public courts are slow and expensive. Merchant courts are fast and inexpensive, they democratize justice 

Resource: https://towardsliberty.com/articles/naddr1qvzqqqr4gupzpdlddzcx9hntfgfw28749pwpu8sw6rj39rx6jw43rdq4pd276vhuqqgrwvm9xa3kxdtpxdjk2e3j8yunvray7sr

6_National tax revenue allocation: 70% to local communities, 30% for national defence (cyber & physical) and energy sovereignty
